    "[14] With this background, this bibliometric analysis aims to find out the research trends on generative AI in breast cancer diagnosis, prognosis and treatment over two decades.",
    "In the preliminary planning stage, search queries were pinpointed and organized as illustrated in Table 1.",
    "These queries were divided into two categories.",
    "Combinations of primary search terms with breast cancer-related items focused on diagnosis and treatment of breast cancer.",
    "The primary search terms encompassed \"AI,\" \"artificial intelligence,\" \"regenerative AI,\" \"responsible AI use,\" \"Machine Learning,\" and a variety of supervised and unsupervised algorithms, as shown in Table 1."
  ]
}